  "title": "Warm Nutty Middle Eastern Lentil Pilaf",
  "description": "A hearty and aromatic one-pot dish featuring red lentils, curry powder, and toasted nuts, inspired by the flavors of the Middle East",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
